A.lyrics:
Chorus: Akâ`usiphathe kuhle Nkosi, busisâ`abagulayo Nkosi!
Busisâ`ilizwe lethu Nkosi, siyacela, siyacela. 1. Abaphethâ`iBandla, akubaphathe kuhle Nkosi;
ubaphâ`amandla , busisâ`abagulayo Nkosi;
ukuze bakukhonze; busisâ`ilizwe lethu Nkosi siyacela. 2. Bumbâ`iBandla lakho, elichithekayo, siphe ukuthula. 3. Qinisâ`ukholo Iwethu, ubekâ`isandla sakho, esithwelâ`usizo.
W. Hlabano

B.lyrics:
1. Babusisiwe, Bazakudla ilifa, abayanga, bazakudla ilifa, emoyeni, bazakudla ilifa.
Chorus: Ngoba umbuso wezulâ`ungowabo.

2. Babusisiwe; abakhalayo; bazaduduzwa;
3. Babusisiwe; abamnene; bomelukulunga;
4. Babusisiwe; abalambela; bomelukulunga; 5. Babusisiwe; abalesihawu; bazahawukelwa.
(c / f Mat 5,1-12; Luka 6,20- 23) M. Majahana

M.lyrics:
Mama Mariya, Nkosikazi yokuthula
Mama wethu.
Siphe, ukuthula mama siphe ukuthula. (2x)
1. Nkosikazi eyetheswa, ngomqhele wenkanyezi;
2. Nina weNdodana kaNkulunkulu, xotsha inzondano lodlakela;
3. Sicelele ukuthula, emulini lelizweni lethu;
4. Mama ugcwele umusa, kuthokoza kwezulu lomhlaba; 5. Msizi wamakholwa, Mvikeli wabahluphekayo;
6. Kwathi igazi lichitheka, elizweni lethu sakhala kuwe; 7. Wahlenga amadodana, lamadodakazi engozini yokufa: 8. Mthombo wokulunga, kakhâ`owadelwa nguwe ecelâ`usizo; 9. Londolozâ`iBandla, duduza abakhalayo, siza abagulayo;
10. Sivuse lapho sisiwa, qinisa ababuthakathaka; 11. Mama siyabonga, sicelele ukuthula, kumntanako
ukuthula. M. Chifana

U.lyrics:
Chorus: UFransisi weAssisi wayeliqhawe lothando
lesibonelo somusa. (2x).
1. Wadela lumhlaba, ngenxa yokuthandâ`uNkulunkulu;
Watshiyâ`abazali, wazinikela eNkosini.
waqoqâ`abangane, baqalisa umhlangano. 2. Watshiya inotho, waba ngumuntukazana,
Konke ayelakho, wakupha abayanga;
Eyakhe inotho, kwakungumthandazo.
3. Wathanda imvelo, kwangathi ingumuntu;
Wayetshumayeza, inyoni zemkhathini;
Ngezidalwa zonke, wadumisâ`uNkulunkulu4. Ngezenzo zakhe,wathandeka eNkosini;
INkosi yambusisa, yamuphâ`amanxeba ayo; Olwakhe udumo, lwadlulâ`olwamakhosi.
A. Gwenelo

W.lyrics:
1. Wozani bantwana, wozani masinya; simbone uJesu uKristu iNkosi. Ovelâ`ezulwini, ofikâ`emhlabeni; ulethe uxolo lomusa lobuhle.
2. Simbone uJesu, elelâ`emgwembeni; simbone luMntwana, omuhle oNgcwele. Wozani sithabe, sithokozisise;
simbone uJesu uMntwana omuhle.

3. E! nangâ`uMariya; emkhonza uJesu; ethaba embona uMntwana omuhle; loJosefâ`oNgcwele, embonga luMntwana; odlulâ`izithunywa ngobuhle lomusa.
4. Zwaninâ`izithunywa, zicula ingoma; zimkhonza luMntwana olelâ`emkhonjeni. Bonanâ`abelusi beguqa kuJesu;
bethaba ngokuba kuzelâ`uMsindisi.
5. Ke lathi sithanda luMntwana omuhle; Simkhonza, simbonga ngengoma ezinhle. Simnikâ`inhliziyo, ahlale nje kizo;
ahlale kakuhle angabâ`esatshiya.
